message.content: <OUTPUT_TEXT>As part of our law office's commitment to efficient and effective legal service, I will oversee and coordinate all activities related to the delivery of subpoenas. This includes ensuring timely issuance, dispatch, and service of subpoenas according to legal requirements and client needs. I will coordinate with process servers and ensure they are informed of all pertinent details to carry out their duties effectively. Regular updates will be provided to our legal team and clients regarding the status of subpoena deliveries to maintain transparency and accountability throughout the legal process.</OUTPUT_TEXT>
